{"type": "root", "attrs": {"icon": "SHELF/makebreakable", "tags": "rigidbodies"}, "body": [{"level": 0, "type": "title", "indent": 0, "text": ["Make Breakable"], "extent": [0, 19]}, {"type": "summary", "indent": 0, "text": ["Automatically fractures an RBD object."], "extent": [67, 113]}, {"level": 2, "id": null, "container": true, "type": "h", "indent": 0, "text": ["Overview"], "extent": [113, 128], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 0, "text": ["This tool creates a ", {"scheme": "Node", "value": "/nodes/dop/voronoifractureconfigureobject", "type": "link", "text": ["Voronoi Fracture Configure Object"], "fullpath": "/nodes/dop/voronoifractureconfigureobject"}, " from an ", {"scheme": "Node", "value": "/nodes/dop/rbdobject", "type": "link", "text": ["RBD Object"], "fullpath": "/nodes/dop/rbdobject"}, " or an ", {"scheme": "Node", "value": "/nodes/dop/rbdpackedobject", "type": "link", "text": ["RBD Packed Object"], "fullpath": "/nodes/dop/rbdpackedobject"}, ", which causes the object to break realistically on impact.  It also creates new objects\nfor any pieces created by fracturing these objects. This is useful for background objects in a scene, since it is a fast and realistic way of breaking an object without having to do anything before hand. If you want more artistic control of the break, you can use the ", {"scheme": null, "value": "/shelf/break", "type": "link", "text": ["Break"], "fullpath": "/shelf/break"}, " or ", {"scheme": null, "value": "/shelf/shatter", "type": "link", "text": ["Shatter"], "fullpath": "/shelf/shatter"}, " tools on the ", {"type": "ui", "text": ["Model"]}, " tab of the shelf. These tools let you prebreak geometry, which you can then make into an ", {"scheme": null, "value": "/shelf/rbdglueobject", "type": "link", "text": ["RBD Glue Object"], "fullpath": "/shelf/rbdglueobject"}, "."], "extent": [128, 874]}]}, {"level": 2, "id": "includeme", "container": true, "type": "h", "indent": 0, "text": ["Using Make Breakable"], "extent": [874, 913], "body": [{"type": "ord_group", "body": [{"blevel": 6, "type": "ord", "indent": 4, "text": ["Select the object you want to break, and click the ", {"scheme": "Icon", "value": "DOP/rbdobject", "type": "link", "text": "", "fullpath": "/shelf/DOP/rbdobject"}, {"scheme": "Node", "value": "/nodes/dop/rbdobject", "type": "link", "text": ["RBD Object"], "fullpath": "/nodes/dop/rbdobject"}, " tool on the ", {"type": "ui", "text": ["Rigid Bodies"]}, " tab."], "extent": [913, 1058], "body": [{"type": "note_group", "body": [{"type": "note", "indent": 8, "role": "item", "extent": [1058, 1072], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 12, "text": ["Once you convert geometry to an RBD object you can only ", {"scheme": null, "value": "/basics/handles_xform", "type": "link", "text": ["transform, rotate, and scale"], "fullpath": "/basics/handles_xform"}, " it when it is on the first frame."], "extent": [1072, 1228]}], "container": true}], "container": true, "role": "item_group"}], "container": true}, {"blevel": 6, "type": "ord", "indent": 4, "text": ["Make sure the new object is selected and click the ", {"scheme": "Icon", "value": "SHELF/makebreakable", "type": "link", "text": "", "fullpath": "/shelf/SHELF/makebreakable"}, {"scheme": "Node", "value": "/nodes/dop/voronoifractureconfigureobject", "type": "link", "text": ["Make Breakable"], "fullpath": "/nodes/dop/voronoifractureconfigureobject"}, " tool on the ", {"type": "ui", "text": ["Rigid Bodies"]}, " tab."], "extent": [1228, 1403]}], "container": true}, {"type": "para", "indent": 4, "text": ["For specific parameter help see the ", {"scheme": "Icon", "value": "SOP/assemble", "type": "link", "text": "", "fullpath": "/shelf/SOP/assemble"}, {"scheme": "Node", "value": "/nodes/dop/voronoifractureconfigureobject", "type": "link", "text": ["Voronoi Fracture\n    Configure Object"], "fullpath": "/nodes/dop/voronoifractureconfigureobject"}, " dynamics node help."], "extent": [1403, 1567]}, {"type": "video_group", "body": [{"ext": null, "type": "video", "indent": 4, "role": "item", "extent": [1567, 1579], "body": [], "container": true, "attrs": {"src": "/videos/shelf/makebreakable.mp4"}}], "container": true, "role": "item_group"}]}, {"level": 1, "id": "related", "container": true, "type": "related_section", "indent": 0, "role": "section", "extent": [1626, 1635], "body": [{"type": "bullet_group", "body": [{"blevel": 6, "type": "bullet", "indent": 4, "text": [{"scheme": "Node", "value": "/nodes/dop/voronoifractureconfigureobject", "type": "link", "text": ["Voronoi Fracture Configure Object"], "fullpath": "/nodes/dop/voronoifractureconfigureobject"}], "extent": [1635, 1717]}, {"blevel": 6, "type": "bullet", "indent": 4, "text": [{"scheme": "Node", "value": "/nodes/dop/voronoifracturesolver", "type": "link", "text": ["Voronoi Fracture Solver"], "fullpath": "/nodes/dop/voronoifracturesolver"}], "extent": [1717, 1780]}, {"blevel": 6, "type": "bullet", "indent": 4, "text": [{"scheme": "Node", "value": "/nodes/dop/voronoifractureparms", "type": "link", "text": ["Voronoi Fracture Parameters"], "fullpath": "/nodes/dop/voronoifractureparms"}], "extent": [1780, 1846]}, {"blevel": 6, "type": "bullet", "indent": 4, "text": [{"scheme": "Node", "value": "/nodes/sop/voronoifracture", "type": "link", "text": ["Voronoi Fracture"], "fullpath": "/nodes/sop/voronoifracture"}], "extent": [1846, 1896]}, {"blevel": 6, "type": "bullet", "indent": 4, "text": [{"scheme": "Node", "value": "/nodes/sop/voronoifracturepoints", "type": "link", "text": ["Voronoi Fracture Points"], "fullpath": "/nodes/sop/voronoifracturepoints"}], "extent": [1896, 1959]}], "container": true}], "text": "Related"}], "title": ["Make Breakable"], "summary": ["Automatically fractures an RBD object."]}